$12M+ value by transforming 20K+  static contracts into the intelligent, searchable “Cargill Brain

AI Augmented Labor Pool replacing shared service center (across procurement and sales contracts) and law firms

50% cost reduction and review time across NDAs, sales and procurement contracts

Context: Duracell’s lean in-house team was spread thin manually reviewing contracts, extracting data, and leveraging expensive outside counsel for overflow contracting support.

Solution: Eudia delivered a fixed-price, fully AI-augmented managed service for Duracell, taking over routine contracts from both the in-house team and external counsel. Eudia ingested historical agreements to build an AI MIND across procurement, data privacy, and more, enabling live review and AI feedback cycles.

Outcome: Review time reduced by 25-80%. MINDs built within 24 hours to power a scalable, efficient contracting engine to support rapid growth with 50% less cost.

Context: A multinational legal team was manually reviewing thousands of external-facing documents for regulatory risks—a slow and costly process.

Solution: In just 2 weeks, Eudia deployed a compliance MIND built on the company’s proprietary frameworks. This compliance brain flagged risks with company-specific accuracy.

Outcome: Within four weeks, the AI achieved above human level accuracy, driving 30% efficiency gains versus manual review. The compliance brain became a repeatable asset for ongoing monitoring and future regulatory needs.

Context: A Fortune 500 company needed to run due diligence on a major acquisition. Nearly 70% of M&A legal spend was tied to routine, commodity analysis.

Solution: Eudia ingested documents from deal data room, processed the documents based on criteria identified for this due diligence analysis and the platform automatically summarized outputs.

Outcome: Reduced DD time from 5 to 2 days . A side-by-side comparison with a top-tier law firm confirmed Eudia’s DD report captured the same critical issues. Costs were reduced, while the knowledge created became reusable intelligence for future deals.

25-80% Reduction in Contract Review Time
"We have been using a legacy software AI review, and this is a step-change improvement. The quality and precision of the redlines is very impressive. We only had to make a few minor edits based on some deal context."

30-50% Reduction in Due Diligence Costs
"Using Eudia in our live M&A deal increased efficiency by 30-50%, enabling us to produce initial risk reports faster and more accurately"

55% Reduction in Review Time
"Wow, the outputs are getting much more nuanced. I’m impressed, and I can tell it’s understanding the data at a new level."
" We probably just would not have done the [deforestation] ask. We would have said that it’s not worth our time and that there’s no way we can do this. My thanks alone isn’t enough!”
